<p>If you would like to help La Marelle fulfil its mission of providing educational and cultural activities to local French-speaking children, please consider the following options.</p>

<h2>Financial Donations</h2>

<p>We are always grateful for donations from companies and individuals. These will be used mainly to help us purchase books and teaching materials for our pupils. We accept the following means of payment:</p>

<p>
-<strong> Cheques</strong> made out to "La Marelle" and sent to 5 Eynsford Road, Greenhithe DA9 9HB.<br />
- <strong>Bank transfers</strong> - please <a href="contact.aspx">contact us</a> for our account details.<br />
- <strong>Paypal</strong> - use the button below to donate using your Paypal account or a credit or debit card.<br />
</p>

<p align="center"><a href="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&hosted_button_id=4215855"><image src="https://www.paypal.com/en_GB/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online."></a></p>


<h2>Donations in kind</h2>

<p>French books and toys, craft and stationery supplies, or general school items are all things we need on a regular basis. We also welcome donations for our fundraisers and raffles. Please <a href="contact.aspx">contact us</a> if you have items you would like to give.</p>

<p>Although we will consider all proposed donations, we may have to decline them if we are not able to store the items or they do not suit our immediate needs.</p>

