<p>Support La Marelle for free when shopping online with over 600 popular retailers, including Argos, NEXT, M&amp;S, John Lewis, Debenhams, HMV, Vodafone, DELL, The Body Shop©, Woolworths, PLAY.com, Interflora, Comet and many more, using <a href="http://www.easyfundraising.org.uk/lamarelle">EasyFundraising</a>.</p>

<p>Raise funds for La Marelle when you search the Web with <a href="http//lamarelle.easysearch.org.uk">EasySearch</a> - the best results from Yahoo!, Windows MSN Live Search and Ask.com in one simple search.
</p>

<h2>Volunteering</h2>

<p>We ask all our pupils' parents to volunteer at the school on a regular basis, but even if you are not a parent, you can help out by volunteering to assist us with fundraising or administrative tasks. Just <a href="Contact.aspx">contact us</a> and we'll no doubt find something for you to do - we will be happy to have you on our team.</p>

